        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-07-02 15:17:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nIt's this commit that is causing the unit tests to fail.\n\nWhen we switched our JMS implementation from HornetQ to ActiveMQ to get rid of security vulnerabilities, the tests for JMS had to be changed to use an embedded ActiveMQ broker. APEX is connecting OK to this embedded broker but is not receiving messages from it. I suspect it is some configuration parameter that is set incorrectly.\n\nI tried to revert this commit but it is failing in Gerrit. Anyway, we'll fix this later today.",
        "patchset_number": 5
      },
